# Package Cancellation & Refund System — Implementation Plan (Rev 3)

Adds agent-defined cancellation policies, customer cancel flow, Razorpay refund, and cancellation email.

---

## Critical Design Decisions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Multi-tenant Razorpay:** Keys always resolved as `booking → package → creator (agent) → razorpay_settings`.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Idempotency:** `BookingRefund.booking_id` unique constraint + `SELECT FOR UPDATE` row lock prevents double-refund.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Payment selection:** Always use `next((p for p in reversed(booking.payments) if p.status == "succeeded"), None)`. Never `payments[-1]`.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Transaction safety:** All DB writes wrapped in `try/except` with `await db.rollback()` on failure — Razorpay refund is called INSIDE the same try block so any failure rolls back DB.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Timezone:** All date math uses `datetime.now(timezone("Asia/Kolkata")).date()`.

