## Verification Plan

| Scenario | Expected |
|---|---|
| Rules out of order | 400 — "descending order" |
| Duplicate daysBefore | 400 — "duplicate values" |
| Cancel 10 days before | 80% of paid amount |
| Cancel 5 days before | 50% of paid amount |
| Cancel 1 day before | 0% |
| Cancel after travel date | 400 — "travel date passed" |
| Cancel twice | 400 — "already cancelled" |
| Razorpay API failure | CANCELLED + refund_status = pending |
| No succeeded payment | CANCELLED + refund_amount = 0 |
